1. Overview

This Software is made publicly available for transparency, security review, research, evaluation, interoperability, and integration with the official deployed PPRF token contract and the broader PaperProof ecosystem. Except for the limited permissions expressly granted in this License, no rights are granted to copy, modify, distribute, sublicense, commercialize, or deploy this Software or any derivative work.

2. Definitions

"Software" means the source code, smart contract code, interface definitions, configuration files, documentation, and other materials in this repository, excluding third-party components that are separately licensed.

"Official Deployed Contract" means the smart contract instance deployed by or under the authority of the copyright holder as the official PPRF token contract of the PaperProof project.

"Permitted Interface Use" means interacting with the Official Deployed Contract, including building software, wallets, explorers, clients, indexers, analytics tools, or frontends that call, query, display, or otherwise interoperate with the Official Deployed Contract through its public interfaces.

"Derivative Work" means any modified, adapted, translated, transformed, or extended version of the Software, and any software substantially based on the protected expression of the Software.

